title: Vowels
content: Learn to read and pronounce the Vietnamese vowels

title: ê
content: /ə̆j/ Similar to 'i' in hi" but shorter. Sometimes pronounced as /ə̯/ as in the 'e' in "dress""

title: i
dateCreated: or after any vowel letter /j/ as in the 'y' in ""yellow""""

title: o
dateUpdated: and /w/ when combined with some other vowels"

title: ơ
content: /ə/ Similar to the last 'a' in Camera"

title: u
dateCreated: or /w/ after 'q' or with some vowel combinations"

title: y
dateCreated: or after any vowel letter /j/ as in the 'y' in "yellow""
